  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study focuses on blood inflammatory markers (pro-inflammatory cytokines,
      anti-inflammatory cytokines, monocytes costimulation molecules) in patients with resistant
      unipolar depression in comparison with non-resistant unipolar depressed patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
