  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  group 1: Patients with resistant MDD (at least 2 failed treatments for the current
             episode) ,current treatment with IRS or IRSNA,

          -  group 2: patients with MDD remission after response to an antidepressant treatment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  comorbid somatic or psychiatric disorders: chronic or acute inflammatory diseases,
             previous treatment with brain stimulation for the current episode, legal protection
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
